WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:23.080 --> 01:24.240
There's a basketball game at school

01:24.240 --> 01:25.640
after school today.

01:25.840 --> 01:26.880
As the hosts,

01:27.000 --> 01:29.039
we should all be there to cheer

01:29.039 --> 01:30.120
for our classmates.

01:30.480 --> 01:31.760
- Okay!
- Okay.

01:33.640 --> 01:35.039
Qingyu, are you going
to the basketball game?

01:35.039 --> 01:36.039
No.

01:38.000 --> 01:39.560
Qiao Qingyu doesn't think of herself

01:39.560 --> 01:41.680
as a member of us.

01:41.680 --> 01:42.600
Indeed.

01:43.610 --> 01:45.020
Come on. The game's about to start.

01:45.500 --> 01:46.250
Let's go.

02:03.170 --> 02:04.380
Hi, welcome.

02:19.130 --> 02:19.660
Thank you.

02:21.300 --> 02:22.020
Please wait.

02:22.450 --> 02:23.620
I'd like a menu, please.

02:25.980 --> 02:26.660
Here's our menu.

02:26.660 --> 02:28.100
See if you like something to drink.

02:32.850 --> 02:34.100
Just water for me, thanks.

02:34.290 --> 02:36.060
Our lemon tea and coffee

02:36.060 --> 02:36.850
are very popular,

02:36.850 --> 02:38.260
and we also have

02:38.260 --> 02:39.010
an afternoon tea set available.

02:39.010 --> 02:40.100
Anything else for you?

02:41.180 --> 02:42.290
She will have a cup of lemon tea.

02:42.490 --> 02:43.010
Got it.

02:47.290 --> 02:48.490
You look exactly alike,

02:49.130 --> 02:50.290
but it seems

02:50.930 --> 02:51.770
your personalities

02:51.770 --> 02:53.340
are worlds apart.

02:53.340 --> 02:55.010
Were you close with Qiao Beiyu?

02:56.010 --> 02:57.290
You asked me out today

02:58.210 --> 02:59.740
to ask about Beiyu, didn't you?

03:03.410 --> 03:08.310
[Episode 6]
[The Rumored Beiyu]

03:11.010 --> 03:12.060
Nanqiao Village is pretty small.

03:13.290 --> 03:15.490
Kids there grow up free and easy,

03:16.130 --> 03:17.930
their days filled with barefoot play
in the mud.

03:18.930 --> 03:19.930
When I was little,

03:20.620 --> 03:22.650
I thought all kids lived like we did,

03:24.340 --> 03:26.340
until I met Beiyu.

03:27.340 --> 03:28.340
Before that,

03:29.060 --> 03:31.180
I had never seen
such a beautiful little girl.

03:31.860 --> 03:32.860
Feihai!

03:33.650 --> 03:35.140
Hi, Jinrui.

03:36.060 --> 03:37.210
This is my cousin, Beiyu.

03:37.420 --> 03:39.060
She will play with us from now on.

03:39.620 --> 03:40.650
Hi, guys.

03:48.020 --> 03:48.740
These are for you.

03:53.300 --> 03:54.140
Thank you.

04:09.250 --> 04:10.740
Day by day,

04:12.060 --> 04:13.740
Beiyu grew more beautiful.

04:15.370 --> 04:17.250
But at some point,

04:17.970 --> 04:19.899
the students at school
started bullying her.

04:22.089 --> 04:23.900
They cruelly accused her
of having no parents, no upbringing,

04:24.580 --> 04:25.530
no manners.

04:27.370 --> 04:30.420
Those rumors spread like wildfire,

04:30.420 --> 04:31.370
infecting everyone.

04:33.650 --> 04:35.650
People often underestimate
the power of gossip.

04:36.300 --> 04:37.650
In a small community,

04:38.620 --> 04:39.930
it's frighteningly easy
to ruin someone's life

04:40.860 --> 04:41.690
with rumors.

04:44.340 --> 04:47.490
When the school found out,
they arranged counseling for her.

04:49.090 --> 04:50.690
I've replayed that time endlessly
in my mind,

04:51.210 --> 04:52.810
wishing I could go back

04:53.250 --> 04:54.460
and choose differently.

04:57.020 --> 04:58.460
But back then,

04:58.970 --> 05:00.770
I was timid and weak.

05:01.620 --> 05:03.530
I just stood by
and watched Beiyu get bullied,

05:04.060 --> 05:06.530
too scared to even step up and help her.

05:07.860 --> 05:08.900
What are you looking at?

05:08.900 --> 05:09.650
What are you staring at?

05:09.930 --> 05:10.690
Huh?

05:10.690 --> 05:12.740
Lost your mind? Pathetic!

05:14.690 --> 05:15.490
Cut it out.

05:17.020 --> 05:17.810
He can't even take a joke.

05:21.180 --> 05:22.020
After graduating high school,

05:22.930 --> 05:24.340
[Mingshidi KTV]
Beiyu moved to Huanzhou

05:24.340 --> 05:25.650
to study at an art school,

05:26.370 --> 05:27.770
and I got into a university there.

05:28.650 --> 05:30.060
We finally left Nanqiao Village.

05:31.340 --> 05:33.620
I went to visit Beiyu once,

05:34.530 --> 05:35.970
but I don't know since when...

05:35.970 --> 05:37.060
I'm not going tomorrow.

05:37.300 --> 05:38.210
She had changed.

05:38.970 --> 05:41.180
She's turned into the person
the rumors described.

05:41.180 --> 05:41.930
What are you looking at?

05:42.450 --> 05:43.890
Stop pretending now.

05:43.890 --> 05:44.300
Come on.

05:45.780 --> 05:47.330
You... You're hurting me.

05:47.330 --> 05:48.250
I said, stop.

05:48.250 --> 05:49.420
Stop pulling me.

05:49.890 --> 05:50.540
What are you doing?

05:50.540 --> 05:50.740
You...

05:54.180 --> 05:55.010
You've got some guts now?

05:57.220 --> 05:57.659
Huh?

05:59.540 --> 06:00.620
Hi, sir!

06:01.570 --> 06:04.060
Keep it down! You might scare her.

06:11.860 --> 06:12.740
After that,

06:14.010 --> 06:15.690
I went abroad as an exchange student.

06:16.010 --> 06:17.540
The next word I heard about Beiyu

06:19.010 --> 06:20.420
was the devastating news of her death.

06:23.010 --> 06:24.420
Did my parents know

06:24.420 --> 06:25.890
that Qiao Beiyu was being bullied?

06:28.810 --> 06:30.420
One day, Beiyu ran away from home

06:31.420 --> 06:32.250
and went to Shunyun.

06:32.890 --> 06:34.450
It was your parents

06:34.450 --> 06:35.860
who sent her back to Nanqiao Village.

06:38.250 --> 06:39.690
So they knew everything,

06:40.620 --> 06:42.130
but instead of saving Beiyu,

06:42.130 --> 06:43.810
they pushed her back into the flames.

06:45.100 --> 06:47.220
I'm sure they had their reasons.

06:49.810 --> 06:52.250
After all, parents always want
what's best for their children.

06:54.659 --> 06:55.810
So you're saying

06:56.180 --> 06:58.370
you had reasons
for letting this happen, too?

06:58.370 --> 06:59.130
No, that's not it.

07:00.130 --> 07:01.570
I've never tried to excuse myself.

07:03.330 --> 07:04.370
Even now, whenever I think about Beiyu,

07:05.930 --> 07:06.860
the guilt is crushing.

07:07.060 --> 07:07.810
What good does that do?

07:08.180 --> 07:09.330
Qiao Beiyu is dead.

07:09.330 --> 07:10.780
She's not coming back to life.

07:11.780 --> 07:12.980
Telling me all this today

07:13.250 --> 07:14.420
is just your way of trying

07:14.420 --> 07:15.370
to ease your own conscience.

07:15.860 --> 07:17.130
You're a hypocrite and a coward.

07:17.130 --> 07:18.540
You're no different

07:18.540 --> 07:19.370
from those who bullied her.

07:19.690 --> 07:20.620
You're just another accomplice.

07:21.370 --> 07:22.010
Qingyu.

07:22.450 --> 07:23.130
Qingyu.

07:25.330 --> 07:26.130
Qingyu.

07:26.810 --> 07:27.620
Qingyu.

07:28.060 --> 07:29.420
Please wait, Qingyu.

07:29.780 --> 07:30.540
Qingyu,

07:30.540 --> 07:30.980
please wait.

07:30.980 --> 07:31.930
What more do you want?

07:33.860 --> 07:36.060
This is a video
of a dance performance Beiyu did

07:36.450 --> 07:37.810
during a school arts showcase

07:37.810 --> 07:38.659
in high school.

07:39.980 --> 07:41.420
I heard it helped her qualify

07:41.659 --> 07:43.450
for the Starry Cup Dance Competition,

07:44.370 --> 07:45.180
though

07:46.740 --> 07:47.930
she never got the chance to participate.

07:49.420 --> 07:50.659
Isn't that Qiao Qingyu?

07:51.690 --> 07:52.659
You're right.

07:52.860 --> 07:54.980
I am hypocritical and cowardly.

07:55.930 --> 07:56.620
That's why

07:57.370 --> 07:58.930
you deserve this more than I do.

08:01.740 --> 08:03.540
She seems so clueless at school,

08:04.010 --> 08:04.740
but there's definitely more to her.

08:05.540 --> 08:06.540
Do you guys still want
to have lunch or not?

08:06.810 --> 08:07.330
Of course.

08:08.100 --> 08:08.930
Well, let's go.

08:09.370 --> 08:09.930
Alright.

08:17.610 --> 08:19.480
[Huanzhou Youth
New Year's Arts Showcase]

08:19.480 --> 08:20.910
[A Dance Tribute to Qiao Beiyu]

10:30.850 --> 10:31.660
Qingyu,

10:32.330 --> 10:33.260
come over and have some water.

10:34.060 --> 10:34.900
I'm not thirsty.

10:37.450 --> 10:38.570
Let your brother take care
of those bowls.

10:38.730 --> 10:39.380
Yu,

10:40.090 --> 10:41.970
help your sister clean up those bowls.

10:41.970 --> 10:42.660
Coming.

10:49.450 --> 10:52.140
Mom, that's not fair.

10:52.140 --> 10:53.540
I already have to deliver takeout

10:53.810 --> 10:55.570
and clean the tables.

10:55.570 --> 10:56.660
And now I have to wash the dishes too?

10:57.900 --> 10:59.780
How am I supposed to do all this?

10:59.970 --> 11:01.810
You can't just make me do

11:01.810 --> 11:02.930
all the work

11:02.930 --> 11:04.180
just because I have bad grades.

11:04.730 --> 11:05.970
Yu!

11:06.930 --> 11:07.730
Yu!

11:08.060 --> 11:08.970
What is it, Dad?

11:09.180 --> 11:09.930
Come.

11:10.380 --> 11:11.180
Deliver this.

11:11.450 --> 11:12.450
Let me do that.

11:15.260 --> 11:16.540
Dad, you saw that, right?

11:16.540 --> 11:18.380
She volunteered to do it.

11:18.380 --> 11:19.180
I'm not slacking off.

11:21.020 --> 11:22.450
Get moving

11:22.450 --> 11:22.970
and wash those dishes, then.

11:23.140 --> 11:23.930
Go.

11:25.330 --> 11:26.140
Okay.

11:27.570 --> 11:28.380
What's going on?

12:05.060 --> 12:05.900
Delivery!

12:06.850 --> 12:08.260
A serving of stir-fried noodles,
no spice.

12:10.060 --> 12:11.850
Anyone here?
I'm from Qiao's Noodle House.

12:19.970 --> 12:20.690
It's eight yuan for the noodles.

12:20.690 --> 12:21.850
I haven't given you your change.

12:22.850 --> 12:24.060
Keep it.

12:56.300 --> 12:56.900
Next,

12:56.900 --> 12:59.020
I need you all to fill in your grades

12:59.020 --> 13:00.500
for each subject in the table

13:00.500 --> 13:03.380
and use the cell
with the automatic average function

13:03.380 --> 13:05.690
to calculate the class average score.

13:06.140 --> 13:08.300
Your classroom performance today

13:08.540 --> 13:10.900
will account for 5% of the final grade.

13:10.930 --> 13:12.260
So, practice carefully.

13:12.690 --> 13:14.060
Alright, let's get started.

13:16.540 --> 13:17.450
Someone posted photos

13:17.450 --> 13:19.020
of Ming Sheng playing basketball
on the School Network.

13:19.300 --> 13:20.690
He looks so handsome!

13:20.690 --> 13:21.900
It's because of those photos

13:22.260 --> 13:24.850
that so many students from other schools
are leaving him messages.

13:24.850 --> 13:25.610
It's so annoying.

13:26.850 --> 13:27.610
But there's nothing we can do.

13:27.610 --> 13:30.660
The info on that site is public.

13:30.660 --> 13:31.900
Anyone can find it with a quick search.

13:36.010 --> 13:37.730
[School Network]

13:48.110 --> 13:51.410
[Huanzhou Art School]

13:56.860 --> 13:59.160
[Xu Mengmeng.
Moments in Huanzhou Art School]

14:07.360 --> 14:10.410
[Xu Mengmeng]

14:15.330 --> 14:16.730
I'm Qiao Beiyu's little sister.

14:16.730 --> 14:17.970
Do you have time to meet up today?

14:25.180 --> 14:25.900
Mr. Sun.

14:25.900 --> 14:26.780
Mr. Li.

14:26.780 --> 14:28.300
I'd like to make an announcement
before you dismiss the class.

14:28.300 --> 14:29.730
Sure, go ahead.

14:29.730 --> 14:31.260
I'll leave them to you.

14:32.570 --> 14:33.930
Alright, everyone,
I have an announcement.

14:34.380 --> 14:36.210
The next two self-study periods

14:36.540 --> 14:38.060
will be changed to chemistry.

14:40.540 --> 14:41.850
What's so surprising about that?

14:41.850 --> 14:43.660
You messed up your midterms.

14:43.660 --> 14:44.540
So, you have no right to whine now.

14:47.130 --> 14:49.460
[Xu Mengmeng: I'm available now.]

14:53.090 --> 14:54.140
Sir, my stomach hurts.

14:54.140 --> 14:55.660
I need to go home.

14:55.780 --> 14:56.970
Can you manage on your own?

14:57.090 --> 14:57.500
Hmm.

14:57.500 --> 14:58.970
Okay. Go home, then.

15:02.060 --> 15:03.330
Pack up your stuff

15:03.500 --> 15:04.330
and head back to class for the lessons.

15:07.380 --> 15:08.300
Sun

15:08.660 --> 15:10.260
is such a softie.

15:10.420 --> 15:12.060
Isn't it obvious she's lying?

15:14.450 --> 15:15.260
Let's just go.

15:18.060 --> 15:18.930
Come on.

15:19.180 --> 15:20.060
Liu,

15:20.850 --> 15:21.660
please don't.

15:22.450 --> 15:24.140
Didn't we agree on this

15:24.140 --> 15:25.500
during our last meal?

15:25.500 --> 15:27.140
Why the sudden change

15:27.140 --> 15:28.570
in giving the lead dancer to Zhang Yue?

15:30.930 --> 15:34.140
I even turned down two gigs for this.

15:34.260 --> 15:37.180
I've got so many expenses to cover.

15:37.690 --> 15:39.300
Can you please help me out?

15:39.690 --> 15:40.970
If I didn't get the lead role,

15:41.380 --> 15:42.930
a small solo part would suffice,

15:42.930 --> 15:45.450
as I'm only 500 yuan short this month.

15:47.730 --> 15:48.380
Alright, Liu,

15:48.380 --> 15:50.500
I'll call you later.

15:50.810 --> 15:51.450
Bye.

15:54.260 --> 15:55.090
Qiao Qingyu?

15:56.660 --> 15:57.450
Sit down please.

16:08.900 --> 16:09.900
Thank you.

16:09.900 --> 16:11.330
Drink up. My treat.

16:11.690 --> 16:12.730
Thank you.

16:13.630 --> 16:15.260
Your sister used to talk about you.

16:15.260 --> 16:16.780
She even showed me your picture.

16:16.900 --> 16:18.380
That's how I recognized you right away.

16:19.090 --> 16:20.570
Qiao Beiyu told you about me?

16:21.970 --> 16:23.300
So, were you two close?

16:24.450 --> 16:25.420
I guess you could say that.

16:25.730 --> 16:28.500
Beiyu appeared cheerful and easygoing,

16:28.900 --> 16:30.260
but I always sensed

16:30.260 --> 16:31.570
a barrier between her and everyone else,

16:31.660 --> 16:32.690
like she was protecting

16:32.690 --> 16:34.140
a significant secret

16:34.140 --> 16:35.450
she didn't want anyone to discover.

16:35.850 --> 16:37.450
Do you know who her boyfriend was?

16:38.900 --> 16:39.730
Boyfriend?

16:48.690 --> 16:50.060
The weather is getting cold.

16:50.660 --> 16:52.020
Beiyu was gorgeous.

16:52.420 --> 16:54.060
She quickly became

16:54.060 --> 16:56.260
the famous beauty of Huanzhou Art School
after starting there.

16:56.500 --> 16:57.610
That clothing store
we talked about last time,

16:58.090 --> 16:59.730
the one with all the pretty outfits.

17:00.610 --> 17:01.900
Let's go this weekend.

17:02.930 --> 17:04.380
Sure, let's go together this weekend.

17:04.540 --> 17:05.260
Okay.

17:05.260 --> 17:06.660
Stop looking at her!

17:07.020 --> 17:09.780
Men in Huanzhou adored her in droves.

17:11.730 --> 17:12.500
Qiao Beiyu.

17:13.300 --> 17:14.660
Someone left something for you.

17:18.690 --> 17:19.609
Thanks, ma'am.

17:20.260 --> 17:22.780
Who's this admirer now?

17:23.260 --> 17:24.609
I'm so jealous.

17:25.140 --> 17:27.609
I wish I had someone
who sent me delicious treats

17:27.609 --> 17:28.180
every day too.

17:29.060 --> 17:30.210
If you like it, it's yours.

17:30.930 --> 17:31.540
Here.

17:32.210 --> 17:33.450
Well then, I'll take it.

17:39.780 --> 17:40.380
Babe!

17:40.380 --> 17:41.380
Hold this, San.

17:43.260 --> 17:44.260
Babe!

17:45.060 --> 17:46.300
Have you been waiting for long?

17:46.300 --> 17:47.180
Yes.

17:47.780 --> 17:48.970
Isn't that Beiyu?

17:49.380 --> 17:51.420
The last guy was riding
a motorcycle, right?

17:51.450 --> 17:53.210
This week, she's found
a new guy with a luxury car.

17:53.380 --> 17:54.420
Why are you so surprised?

17:54.500 --> 17:55.780
She's beautiful.

17:55.780 --> 17:57.020
There are plenty of men courting her.

17:57.020 --> 17:57.610
It's normal.

18:03.060 --> 18:04.020
Unfortunately,

18:04.020 --> 18:06.260
all she met were rogues.

19:12.570 --> 19:15.330
Let's go have some hotpot later.

19:15.780 --> 19:16.570
Let me comb your hair first.

19:16.570 --> 19:17.570
And then, we'll go have a hotpot.

19:17.980 --> 19:18.810
Die!

19:22.980 --> 19:24.220
What are you doing?

19:24.610 --> 19:25.570
I've made it clear to you.

19:25.570 --> 19:27.090
We've broken up!

19:27.260 --> 19:27.890
What?

19:29.410 --> 19:30.060
Seriously?

19:30.300 --> 19:31.540
You wanted to break up,

19:31.540 --> 19:32.610
but did I say yes?

19:32.940 --> 19:34.780
Tell me, did I say yes?

19:34.980 --> 19:35.780
Beat him up!

19:35.980 --> 19:36.810
No...

19:36.810 --> 19:38.540
Don't hurt him!

19:38.540 --> 19:39.980
If you don't stop, I'll call the police!

19:39.980 --> 19:41.130
Stop!

19:41.130 --> 19:41.780
Hei!

19:41.780 --> 19:42.500
Qiao Beiyu.

19:42.500 --> 19:43.060
I'm sorry, Hei!

19:43.060 --> 19:43.980
I'm going to slap you
if you walk over there.

19:43.980 --> 19:44.850
Hei!

19:48.370 --> 19:49.170
Hei.

19:49.740 --> 19:50.610
I'm sorry.

19:50.610 --> 19:52.060
I didn't know she was your girl.

19:57.370 --> 19:58.850
She came onto me first.

20:04.810 --> 20:06.170
Shut your mouth!

20:06.170 --> 20:06.780
Shut it!

20:12.940 --> 20:13.610
Well, well.

20:14.410 --> 20:15.060
Come.

20:15.260 --> 20:16.370
Listen to him.

20:16.370 --> 20:17.740
Did you hear what he said?

20:17.740 --> 20:18.780
He said

20:18.780 --> 20:19.220
you came onto him.

20:21.060 --> 20:21.940
I like you so much.

20:21.940 --> 20:22.740
So much.

20:23.090 --> 20:24.540
And you cheated on me.

20:24.540 --> 20:26.500
What will people say about me now?

20:26.500 --> 20:27.300
What will they think of me?

20:28.090 --> 20:28.890
Tell me!

20:29.780 --> 20:30.570
Tell me!

20:33.370 --> 20:34.170
You want to humiliate me, right?

20:34.170 --> 20:35.810
Okay, I'm dragging you down with me.

20:35.810 --> 20:37.700
Come here.

20:37.700 --> 20:38.330
Look at her.

20:38.330 --> 20:39.500
Her name is Qiao Beiyu.

20:39.500 --> 20:40.740
Don't touch me!

20:45.260 --> 20:47.090
Your sister seemed sharp,

20:47.090 --> 20:48.500
but she was surprisingly easy to fool.

20:48.700 --> 20:50.980
If a guy even showed
her a little kindness,

20:51.260 --> 20:52.780
she'd fall head over heels for him

20:52.780 --> 20:54.060
and give him her whole heart.

20:54.940 --> 20:55.980
The more she loved,

20:56.780 --> 20:58.890
the more those men thought
they could take advantage of her,

20:59.130 --> 21:00.330
and the harder they hurt her.

21:04.500 --> 21:05.650
You're finally back.

21:05.850 --> 21:07.370
Ms. Tang asked about you today.

21:07.500 --> 21:08.460
She said if you skip class again,

21:08.460 --> 21:09.980
you'll fail this semester.

21:10.650 --> 21:11.740
I'm honestly speechless.

21:11.740 --> 21:13.650
I've never seen anyone get
so caught up in a relationship like you.

21:17.090 --> 21:17.890
What's up?

21:19.850 --> 21:20.650
Let me see.

21:22.370 --> 21:23.170
Who did this?

21:23.170 --> 21:24.500
Come on, let's report it to the police.

21:25.170 --> 21:26.650
We can't go to the police.

21:28.330 --> 21:29.850
You broke up with him.

21:32.370 --> 21:33.540
I don't get it.

21:37.060 --> 21:40.090
Why does every guy treat me like this?

21:40.260 --> 21:42.500
I've done so much for them.

21:43.540 --> 21:45.540
Mengmeng, is it all my fault?

21:46.850 --> 21:48.060
Maybe I

21:49.300 --> 21:51.850
don't deserve to be treated well.

21:52.090 --> 21:54.260
Qiao Beiyu, what are you talking about?

21:54.460 --> 21:55.740
Will you snap out of it?

21:55.740 --> 21:57.500
I know there's something wrong with me,

21:59.780 --> 22:01.130
but I can't help it.

22:06.780 --> 22:08.500
I just can't.

22:08.780 --> 22:10.780
I can't control myself.

22:14.260 --> 22:16.060
But Beiyu acted as if under a spell.

22:16.300 --> 22:17.700
She kept dating scumbags,

22:18.060 --> 22:19.130
and despite my reasoning

22:19.130 --> 22:19.980
and even scolding,

22:19.980 --> 22:20.780
nothing worked.

22:21.500 --> 22:24.170
Did any of her boyfriends
come from Nanqiao Village?

22:27.060 --> 22:31.410
I remember her mentioning
someone from her hometown.

22:31.410 --> 22:32.330
What's his name?

22:33.500 --> 22:35.300
She had so many admirers.

22:35.300 --> 22:36.300
I can't remember.

22:44.890 --> 22:47.700
How about this? I'll ask around.

22:47.700 --> 22:49.090
If I find anything, I'll let you know.

22:49.090 --> 22:49.940
You should go home soon

22:49.940 --> 22:51.260
so your parents won't worry.

22:52.890 --> 22:53.850
Check please!

22:54.980 --> 22:55.780
Mengmeng.

22:57.460 --> 22:59.300
If Qiao Beiyu were still alive,

22:59.700 --> 23:02.060
do you think she would have
become a dancer like you?

23:13.260 --> 23:14.850
Did you ever see Beiyu dance?

23:17.090 --> 23:18.570
Whenever the music started

23:19.260 --> 23:21.500
her movements

23:21.850 --> 23:23.740
made her radiant.

23:25.500 --> 23:27.890
Her performance was the best
in our class.

23:28.500 --> 23:30.130
She'd never end up like me,

23:30.130 --> 23:31.980
struggling in a second-rate troupe.

23:33.700 --> 23:34.700
Beiyu used to say

23:35.060 --> 23:36.170
that after graduation,

23:36.170 --> 23:37.500
she wanted to keep studying

23:37.940 --> 23:40.090
and eventually join
a professional dance company

23:40.370 --> 23:41.940
to become a top performer.

24:07.260 --> 24:09.060
Hi, are these your takeouts?

24:09.410 --> 24:10.060
No.

24:11.300 --> 24:13.500
Hi, are these your takeouts?

24:15.780 --> 24:16.570
Over here.

24:25.890 --> 24:26.850
What are you up to now?

24:27.570 --> 24:28.460
Nothing.

24:28.980 --> 24:30.700
I just thought
we could help each other out.

24:31.370 --> 24:33.460
Her family runs a noodle shop,

24:33.460 --> 24:34.740
and we haven't had lunch yet.

24:34.850 --> 24:35.980
I just wanted to support their business.

24:36.170 --> 24:38.540
Plus, it keeps some shady people
with too much money

24:38.540 --> 24:40.500
from harassing them. Am I right?

24:43.260 --> 24:44.540
A serving of stir-fried noodles,
no spice,

24:44.540 --> 24:46.330
and two servings of beef noodles.
That's 26 yuan.

24:47.740 --> 24:48.500
Hold on.

24:48.500 --> 24:49.500
What's with your attitude?

24:49.850 --> 24:51.500
Remember who's paying.

24:52.090 --> 24:52.890
Is this how you treat customers?

24:52.890 --> 24:53.780
Don't you want to make money?

24:54.130 --> 24:55.890
I might not be as wealthy as you,

24:55.890 --> 24:56.890
but I'm not a deadbeat.

24:57.090 --> 24:59.330
Who are you accusing of skipping out?

25:00.700 --> 25:01.500
Here's your money.

25:04.090 --> 25:05.740
Take the noodles back.
I'm returning them.

25:11.300 --> 25:12.780
Come on, let it go.

25:12.780 --> 25:13.850
Just let it go.

25:14.460 --> 25:15.300
Alright?

25:18.130 --> 25:20.170
Here's 30 yuan. Keep the change.

25:22.260 --> 25:23.850
I might not have money,
but I don't take advantage of people.

25:27.940 --> 25:30.090
Why does she always
have to be so standoffish?

25:31.980 --> 25:33.650
Sorry, it slipped out of my hands.

25:33.650 --> 25:35.020
Sheng, perfect timing.

25:35.020 --> 25:35.540
Let's eat.

26:23.300 --> 26:24.330
What's the matter, Qiao Qingyu?

26:25.090 --> 26:26.330
Do you know how to say thank you?

26:29.060 --> 26:29.850
Thank you.

26:32.060 --> 26:32.850
You're welcome.

26:34.500 --> 26:35.260
To repay the favor,

26:35.260 --> 26:36.940
and since it's on your way home,

26:38.260 --> 26:39.260
give me a ride.

26:40.570 --> 26:41.700
No way.

27:20.850 --> 27:21.700
Qiao Qingyu.

27:23.740 --> 27:25.370
Well...

27:26.060 --> 27:27.980
Who was that guy
at the café the other day?

27:30.020 --> 27:31.060
I know.

27:31.850 --> 27:32.980
Was he your sister's boyfriend?

27:33.060 --> 27:33.850
No.

27:35.260 --> 27:37.570
Then, he must be
a close friend of your sister's.

27:46.780 --> 27:47.700
Are you okay?

28:00.610 --> 28:01.610
So your sister developed

28:01.610 --> 28:03.370
a twisted mindset

28:03.370 --> 28:04.650
after being hurt by her first love.

28:05.170 --> 28:06.570
Any kindness from a man

28:06.570 --> 28:08.570
triggered pathological dependence
in her,

28:08.980 --> 28:10.460
causing her to give
her whole heart away.

28:11.370 --> 28:13.060
I'll find the one responsible

28:13.060 --> 28:14.090
and get justice for her.

28:23.370 --> 28:24.260
It's raining.

28:26.300 --> 28:27.170
Hold on tight.

28:44.380 --> 28:47.380
♪You opened a window♪

28:50.370 --> 28:54.310
♪I saw hope outside the window♪

28:56.480 --> 29:00.520
♪You said something
I couldn't understand♪

29:02.300 --> 29:05.780
♪And I realized my desire♪

29:17.170 --> 29:17.980
What's going on?

29:21.460 --> 29:23.220
Why is this still with you?

29:24.170 --> 29:25.610
Wasn't it already taken care of?

29:26.500 --> 29:27.700
Someone gave it to me.

29:28.980 --> 29:29.850
Who gave it to you?

29:30.980 --> 29:31.500
Qiao Qingyu,

29:31.500 --> 29:33.220
why are you keeping it?

29:34.260 --> 29:35.500
Will it help with your studies

29:35.500 --> 29:37.020
or improve your grades?

29:38.780 --> 29:40.780
No more keeping useless things!

29:41.220 --> 29:42.500
This isn't useless.

29:42.500 --> 29:44.090
It's a video of Qiao Beiyu dancing.

29:47.220 --> 29:48.570
You want to learn to dance now too?

29:55.650 --> 29:56.460
Go ahead, I dare you!

29:58.020 --> 29:59.300
I won't stand by

29:59.300 --> 30:01.170
and watch you end up like your sister.

30:30.980 --> 30:34.090
- Go!
- Go!

30:38.700 --> 30:41.810
- Go!
- Go!

30:43.940 --> 30:45.890
- Go!
- Go!

31:17.300 --> 31:18.220
Sheng.

31:19.850 --> 31:22.370
Shredded potatoes, Kung Pao chicken,
sweet and sour ribs.

31:23.170 --> 31:24.060
No. I'm not hungry.

31:30.370 --> 31:31.460
You were fine during our practice.

31:31.460 --> 31:32.570
How did you suddenly catch a cold?

31:33.220 --> 31:33.980
Yes.

31:34.300 --> 31:35.780
You left without saying a word.

31:37.780 --> 31:39.700
Were you off doing
something you shouldn't have?

31:43.260 --> 31:43.890
Hey!

31:44.650 --> 31:45.460
Shut up.

32:22.120 --> 32:23.900
[Qiao Beiyu: I'm trapped.
I don't deserve this.]

32:23.900 --> 32:24.370
[Difficulty fuels desire.]

32:24.370 --> 32:24.830
[Years of practice, moments of glory.]

32:24.830 --> 32:28.310
[Qiao Beiyu's Album]

32:52.440 --> 32:54.060
[Hei]

32:54.060 --> 32:55.610
Qiao Beiyu's pretty little sister,

32:55.610 --> 32:56.810
I heard you're looking for me.

32:57.700 --> 32:58.500
Who are you?

33:01.610 --> 33:03.020
I'm your brother-in-law.

33:03.850 --> 33:05.370
Are you from Nanqiao Village?

33:08.610 --> 33:09.570
You want to find out?

33:09.810 --> 33:10.610
Let's meet up.

33:11.300 --> 33:12.220
Don't worry.

33:12.220 --> 33:13.780
I'll take good care of you.

33:24.570 --> 33:27.090
Fang, have you thought about

33:27.090 --> 33:28.370
what I mentioned last time?

33:29.610 --> 33:30.610
What was it about?

33:31.610 --> 33:34.220
My neighbor's youngest son.
Don't you remember?

33:38.890 --> 33:40.220
I don't think we're a good match.

33:40.610 --> 33:41.740
Why not?

33:41.740 --> 33:43.610
Tall, handsome,

33:43.610 --> 33:44.570
with a house, a car,

33:44.570 --> 33:45.610
and a stable job. He's got it all.

33:45.810 --> 33:47.410
He was studying abroad for a long time,

33:47.410 --> 33:48.890
which is why he's late in settling down.

33:49.570 --> 33:50.850
You're not getting any younger.

33:50.850 --> 33:51.650
I have something to do, ma'am.

33:51.650 --> 33:52.410
Remember to sign the paper.

33:52.410 --> 33:52.940
I'll pick it up later.

33:52.940 --> 33:53.700
You should really think about it.

33:54.220 --> 33:55.170
Don't miss this chance.

33:55.810 --> 33:56.610
Are you here to see your dad?

34:00.890 --> 34:01.700
Are you okay?

34:07.220 --> 34:08.020
Are you ill?

34:13.170 --> 34:14.780
The blood test results are back.

34:14.780 --> 34:15.500
Everything's normal.

34:17.699 --> 34:18.699
Here, the thermometer.

34:24.850 --> 34:26.699
37.1 degrees.

34:26.699 --> 34:27.610
Nothing to worry about.

34:28.260 --> 34:29.090
I told you,

34:29.090 --> 34:30.570
it's just a mild cold.

34:30.780 --> 34:32.570
You insisted on running all these tests.

34:32.650 --> 34:34.500
Fine, I was worrying for nothing.

34:34.889 --> 34:37.370
Here, this is porridge,
and these are your meds.

34:37.370 --> 34:38.610
Make sure to take them on time.

34:41.330 --> 34:42.500
Got it. I'll head out now.

34:44.570 --> 34:47.090
Oh, and don't tell that guy.

34:47.090 --> 34:48.330
I don't want to hear his nagging.

34:48.460 --> 34:49.460
I know what to do.

34:49.940 --> 34:50.889
Thanks, Ms. Fang.

34:51.570 --> 34:52.500
Get some rest.

34:52.540 --> 34:53.330
Got it.

34:56.130 --> 34:57.460
I'm over ten years older than him.

34:57.980 --> 34:59.540
Why won't he call me ma'am?

35:02.980 --> 35:05.130
The surgery for bed 37
has been rescheduled to the afternoon.

35:05.980 --> 35:07.260
How did the surgery go?

35:10.090 --> 35:12.170
The patient had a sudden hemorrhage
during the operation.

35:12.170 --> 35:13.300
Luckily, Dr. Li and I

35:13.300 --> 35:14.500
quickly located the bleeding point.

35:14.850 --> 35:16.540
I'd say it was a success.

35:19.850 --> 35:21.570
Where is Ming Sheng? Did he leave?

35:22.260 --> 35:23.060
He's left.

35:24.300 --> 35:26.540
I gave him everything you asked me to.

35:27.180 --> 35:30.460
He told me not
to let you know he was here.

35:32.650 --> 35:33.900
That brat.

35:34.290 --> 35:35.250
You and your son

35:35.250 --> 35:36.540
are very much alike, you know,

35:36.940 --> 35:38.380
stubborn and always saying one thing

35:38.460 --> 35:39.460
but meaning another.

35:41.940 --> 35:43.540
Like father, like son.

35:45.130 --> 35:46.770
You've worked hard these days,

35:46.770 --> 35:49.250
looking after Ming Sheng.

35:50.980 --> 35:52.060
Worked hard?

35:52.060 --> 35:53.060
Come on, it's nothing.

35:54.460 --> 35:55.690
I get to play the good cop, after all.

36:05.650 --> 36:06.460
Oh, right.

36:07.860 --> 36:09.460
My parents are coming to Huanzhou
this weekend.

36:09.690 --> 36:10.940
Want to have a meal together?

36:15.290 --> 36:17.170
I understand if you don't want
to make our relationship public.

36:17.170 --> 36:18.540
I've explained it to them,

36:18.900 --> 36:20.380
and they'll keep it a secret.

36:20.650 --> 36:22.340
It's just a meal,

36:22.340 --> 36:23.090
nothing more.

36:23.090 --> 36:23.540
Oh.

36:33.130 --> 36:33.940
Sure.

36:34.460 --> 36:35.460
Let's have a meal together.

36:41.170 --> 36:42.460
Hurry up and eat.
Get some rest afterward.

37:01.540 --> 37:02.340
Qiao Qingyu.

37:05.090 --> 37:06.250
Who are you?

37:08.340 --> 37:10.290
Didn't we have a nice chat online?

37:10.650 --> 37:11.940
How could you forget me so quickly?

37:12.540 --> 37:13.860
You're Hei?

37:14.060 --> 37:15.290
That's right.

37:15.290 --> 37:16.650
Come on, let's have a chat.

37:17.570 --> 37:18.900
I need to get home now.

37:18.900 --> 37:19.860
Hold on.

37:21.060 --> 37:22.020
Weren't you

37:22.020 --> 37:23.290
the one asking around about Hei?

37:23.290 --> 37:24.340
Now you're pretending
to be all innocent?

37:24.900 --> 37:26.460
My mom's waiting for me at home.

37:27.500 --> 37:29.170
What's the rush?

37:29.340 --> 37:30.340
What's the fun in that?

37:30.650 --> 37:32.770
How about this?
I'll treat you to something nice

37:32.900 --> 37:35.090
and relaxing.
How does that sound?

37:36.170 --> 37:38.340
I heard there's a good bubble tea shop
across the street.

37:38.340 --> 37:39.380
Let's go there and talk.

37:39.380 --> 37:39.900
Bubble tea shop?

37:39.900 --> 37:41.690
They don't look like good people.

37:41.690 --> 37:42.210
Sure.

37:42.730 --> 37:44.380
It's too risky to get involved
with those thugs.

37:44.420 --> 37:45.420
Yes, let's go.

37:45.420 --> 37:47.170
Let's go
before the evening bus rush starts.

37:56.690 --> 37:58.250
This is your usual hangout?

37:59.170 --> 38:00.610
This place
doesn't look all that special.

38:02.380 --> 38:03.020
Listen up,

38:03.170 --> 38:04.130
today,

38:04.130 --> 38:06.210
everything is
on Qiao Qingyu's friend, Hei.

38:06.210 --> 38:08.420
Order away.

38:08.420 --> 38:09.250
Give us the table.

38:11.380 --> 38:12.770
Come on, it's my treat.

38:13.460 --> 38:14.650
You know Qiao Qingyu, right?

38:15.210 --> 38:17.250
Take a seat.

38:26.130 --> 38:26.940
Here.

38:34.040 --> 38:35.060
Not bad.

38:35.520 --> 38:37.060
I like bubble tea too.

38:38.160 --> 38:38.980
Help yourself.

38:39.040 --> 38:39.860
I'll order more for you if you like.

38:42.400 --> 38:44.090
From now on,
I'm going to call you "Babe."

38:44.960 --> 38:46.500
That's what I used to call your sister.

38:48.340 --> 38:50.420
How did you meet Qiao Beiyu?

38:51.040 --> 38:52.570
A classic case
of the hero saving the damsel.

38:54.840 --> 38:56.020
Outside a karaoke bar,

38:56.280 --> 38:57.690
some guy was harassing her,

38:57.800 --> 38:59.420
and I stepped in to settle it.

39:00.360 --> 39:01.800
Back when she was at art school,

39:01.960 --> 39:03.560
your sister loved to sing.

39:04.320 --> 39:05.920
She often hung out at my karaoke place.

39:05.920 --> 39:06.960
I looked out for her.

39:08.160 --> 39:09.480
Over time,

39:10.840 --> 39:12.280
we got together.

39:13.920 --> 39:15.160
Honestly,

39:15.160 --> 39:17.480
your sister was really beautiful.

39:17.480 --> 39:19.120
How could someone like me
end up with her?

39:19.960 --> 39:21.720
It was like hitting the jackpot.

39:21.720 --> 39:23.640
Of course, I treated her well.

39:24.360 --> 39:27.080
Eventually, I really fell for her.

39:27.640 --> 39:28.760
Whatever she said, I'd agree to it.

39:30.480 --> 39:32.520
But over time, it wasn't
what I thought it would be.

39:33.240 --> 39:34.560
She wasn't as good as I thought she was.

39:34.880 --> 39:36.760
Your sister was nothing but dumb!

39:37.880 --> 39:40.320
She believed whatever any guy told her.

39:40.520 --> 39:42.960
As long as it was a man,
she'd believe it.

39:45.040 --> 39:46.240
Come a little closer.

39:47.520 --> 39:48.560
I didn't scare you, did I?

39:48.840 --> 39:50.240
Whenever I talk about your sister,

39:51.680 --> 39:52.640
I get so worked up.

39:54.120 --> 39:55.160
But I can tell,

39:55.520 --> 39:56.720
you're different from her.

39:59.080 --> 40:00.000
You're

40:01.440 --> 40:02.840
the pure type.

40:02.840 --> 40:04.080
Do you have a boyfriend?

40:04.080 --> 40:05.840
So you met her in Huanzhou?

40:06.440 --> 40:07.280
That's right.

40:07.520 --> 40:08.440
Then I've got the wrong person.

40:08.440 --> 40:09.200
That's not right.

40:09.200 --> 40:10.440
Sit down and listen.

40:10.800 --> 40:12.440
You didn't get the wrong person.

40:13.120 --> 40:14.160
It's fate.

40:14.240 --> 40:15.360
I'm exactly who you're looking for.

40:15.960 --> 40:17.520
You know, I saw you years ago.

40:17.520 --> 40:19.040
When did I ever meet you?

40:19.040 --> 40:19.840
When?

40:21.120 --> 40:23.120
Outside the art school.
Try to recall it.

40:37.600 --> 40:40.160
Baby!

40:40.160 --> 40:42.520
I've been waiting. Give me a hug.

40:44.800 --> 40:46.960
I bought you flowers. Do you like them?

40:48.880 --> 40:49.680
Thanks.

40:49.760 --> 40:51.400
Don't mention it.

40:51.880 --> 40:53.280
You must be tired
of all those lessons today.

40:53.840 --> 40:54.480
Are you tired?

40:54.480 --> 40:55.280
It's all right.

40:56.000 --> 40:57.400
Let's go. I'm starving.

40:57.400 --> 40:59.560
Come, we are having seafood.

40:59.560 --> 41:00.680
Come. Get the car started.

41:01.720 --> 41:04.120
Qiao Beiyu!

41:04.120 --> 41:07.720
[Huanzhou Art School]

41:07.800 --> 41:09.360
I'm in Huanzhou for the IMO.

41:09.440 --> 41:12.120
Mom wants you to have the fruits.

41:12.760 --> 41:13.680
Who are you?

41:14.360 --> 41:15.880
I don't know you.

41:17.200 --> 41:18.640
You must be her sister back home.

41:19.000 --> 41:20.560
I said I don't know her.

41:20.720 --> 41:21.560
Let's go.

41:21.960 --> 41:22.520
I'm starving.

41:22.600 --> 41:23.640
I can see the resemblance.

41:23.960 --> 41:25.120
I told you, I don't know her.

41:29.880 --> 41:30.600
Babe...

41:30.920 --> 41:31.280
Qiao Beiyu!

41:32.000 --> 41:33.200
I don't know you either,
and I never will.

41:35.600 --> 41:38.400
You know, I've always
cared about you the most.

41:40.200 --> 41:41.040
Drive faster.

41:47.720 --> 41:50.080
I actually understood
what your sister was thinking back then.

41:50.520 --> 41:51.600
She was

41:51.600 --> 41:52.440
protecting you.

41:53.160 --> 41:54.480
You were so young.

41:55.640 --> 41:58.240
She didn't want you to have
anything to do with someone like me.

41:58.440 --> 41:59.440
But it didn't matter

41:59.880 --> 42:02.440
because now we know each other,
and it's not too late.

42:04.640 --> 42:09.160
And look at you, all grown up

42:09.840 --> 42:10.880
and beautiful!

42:10.880 --> 42:11.440
Don't touch me!

42:11.440 --> 42:12.480
So what if I'm touching you?

42:12.480 --> 42:13.280
Stay away from me!

42:13.280 --> 42:13.920
No!

42:14.360 --> 42:15.000
Don't touch me!

42:15.000 --> 42:15.640
Hey, what are you doing?

42:15.880 --> 42:17.120
From now on, you're mine.

42:17.120 --> 42:18.520
You'll be paying back
what your sister owed me.

42:49.950 --> 42:53.640
♪Perhaps♪

42:54.150 --> 42:59.850
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

43:00.990 --> 43:06.390
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

43:07.390 --> 43:12.950
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

43:18.620 --> 43:22.290
♪In the future♪

43:22.750 --> 43:28.470
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

43:29.970 --> 43:35.040
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

43:36.290 --> 43:41.450
♪That never expires♪

43:45.050 --> 43:49.520
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

43:50.520 --> 43:54.190
♪Is your name♪

43:54.690 --> 43:59.790
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

44:00.870 --> 44:04.090
♪At first sight♪

44:04.520 --> 44:07.800
♪The future has been determined♪

44:08.490 --> 44:14.050
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

44:15.150 --> 44:18.690
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

44:19.150 --> 44:23.090
♪Is a place♪

44:23.390 --> 44:28.950
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

44:29.620 --> 44:32.990
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

44:33.320 --> 44:36.790
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

44:37.320 --> 44:43.390
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
